Name:               tagged-exception-core
Version:            1.0.0.0
Synopsis:           Reflect exceptions using phantom types.
Description:
  This library provides interface similar to /extensible-exceptions/.  It
  introduces 'MonadException' class, which uses phantom types to tag code that
  may raise exception.  Intention is to make exceptions explicit and to
  enforce exception handling.
